item.description:
Singles Dance

Event: Singles Dance featuring DJ Paul R. "Playing dance tunes from the 80s, 90s and contemporary freestyle music"

Host: Ozzie Tuiskula~~~~~774 262-0075~~~~~ danceworcester@aol.com

Web site: www.danceworcester.net

Cost: $10.00
Date & Start Time: Nov. 7th from 7:30pm till 12:00am
Where: Maironis Park~ 52 S. Quinsigamond Ave ~ Shrewsbury, Mass.

Cash bar. Coffee, and light refreshments provided. Please dress nicely. No jeans.

During the cold and inclimate weather, we will be providing complimentary shuttle service. This service will be provide between 7:30pm and 9:00pm. We will do transport between the parking lot and ballroom entrance. Grey mini van with emergency lights flashing will be driven by my daughter's friend. You will be identified leaving your parking lights on. Van holds 6 besides driver.
